description: This app has come in really handy for making app mockups and concepts, especially in conjunction with Inkscape. Also great for app developers as I've heard, but haven't really used it that way yet.
summary: Neat little app, great for mockups

description: It's really useful when developing an app. You can find the icons preinstalled on your operating system, and more.
Instructions are included to use icons in an app, or in your system! You can even use the icons directly as SVG by saving to a folder. Thanks for developing this!
summary: Really useful app, no matter what you are developing!

description: This is perfect for developement, but more icons should be added and it should improve tags.
As Glade often lacks a good search for icons i really appreciate this application as it helps to find icons quickly!
